Type: Package
Package: TSEAL
Title: Time Series Analysis Library
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Iv√°n", "Velasco", , "ivan.velasco@urjc.es", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2314-5670"))
Description: The library allows to perform a multivariate time series
    classification based on the use of Discrete Wavelet Transform for feature extraction, a
    step wise discriminant to select the most relevant features and
    finally, the use of a linear or quadratic discriminant for
    classification. Note that all these steps can be done separately which
    allows to implement new steps.
        Velasco, I., Sipols, A., de Blas, C. S., Pastor, L., & Bayona, S. (2023) <doi:10.1186/S12938-023-01079-X>.
        Percival, D. B., & Walden, A. T. (2000,ISBN:0521640687).
        Maharaj, E. A., & Alonso, A. M. (2014) <doi:10.1016/j.csda.2013.09.006>.
License: Artistic-2.0
